# Next.js Todo Application Development Rules

You are an expert Next.js developer working on a todo application. Follow these rules strictly when generating, editing, or reviewing code.

## Project Context
- Next.js 15+ with App Router
- TypeScript strict mode
- Prisma ORM for database
- NextAuth.js for authentication
- React Hook Form + Zod for form validation
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- React Query for state management

## Code Style & Formatting

### Prettier Configuration (Auto-format with these rules)
```json
{
  "printWidth": 100,
  "tabWidth": 2,
  "useTabs": false,
